  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 20th level, you gain the ability to harness extraordinary martial prowess. As a bonus action, you can magically become an avatar of conquest, gaining the following benefits for 1 minute:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You have resistance to all damage.</li>\n<li>When you take the Attack action on your turn, you can make one additional attack as part of that action.</li>\n<li>Your melee weapon attacks score a critical hit on a roll of 19 or 20 on the d20.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest, unless you expend a 5th-level spell slot to use it again.</p>",
